
✅ Nicehash API server running on http://localhost:8080

📊 ACCOUNTING endpoints:
   GET  //main/api/v2/account                - Account info
   GET  //main/api/v2/balances               - Multi-currency balances
   GET  //main/api/v2/balance/:currency      - Balance for currency
   GET  //main/api/v2/activities             - All activities
   GET  //main/api/v2/activities/:currency   - Activities for currency
   GET  //main/api/v2/currencies             - Available currencies
   GET  //main/api/v2/deposits               - All deposits
   GET  //main/api/v2/deposits/:currency     - Deposits for currency

⛏️  MINING endpoints:
   GET  //main/api/v2/mining/rigs            - All mining rigs
   GET  //main/api/v2/mining/rigs/activeWorkers - Active workers
   GET  //main/api/v2/mining/rigs/:rigId     - Rig details
   GET  //main/api/v2/mining/rig/stats/algo  - Rig stats by algorithm
   GET  //main/api/v2/mining/rig/stats/unpaid - Unpaid statistics
   GET  //main/api/v2/mining/stats/algo      - Miner stats by algorithm
   GET  //main/api/v2/mining/rigs/payouts    - Payouts
   GET  //main/api/v2/mining/rigs/stats/data - Daily earnings
   GET  //main/api/v2/mining/rigs/stats/data/algo - Daily earnings per algo
   GET  //main/api/v2/mining/rigs/stats/history - Earnings history
   GET  //main/api/v2/mining/groups          - Mining groups
   GET  //main/api/v2/mining/algorithms      - Mining algorithms
   GET  //main/api/v2/mining/markets         - Mining markets

🌐 PUBLIC endpoints:
   GET  //main/api/v2/public/currencies      - Public currencies
   GET  //main/api/v2/public/fees            - Fee information

🏊 POOLS endpoints:
   GET  ////main/api/v2/pool/                  - List all pools
   GET  ////main/api/v2/pool//:poolId          - Pool details
   POST ////main/api/v2/pool/                  - Create/Edit pool
   POST ////main/api/v2/pool//verify           - Verify pool
   DELETE ////main/api/v2/pool//:poolId        - Delete pool

⚙️  CONFIG endpoints:
   GET  //main/api/v2/config                 - Get tool config
   POST //main/api/v2/config                 - Save tool config

